Receipt Creation Interface will be responsible for posting transactions into WarehouseLogic and creating receipts.

Receipt Creation Interface creates ‘U’ (not all required inventory level presented) and ‘P’ (all required inventory levels presented) type of receipt lines. The uniqueness of Customer Reference Number will be validated. Duplicate Receipts will be rejected.
R (at least one detail record is required)

This value will be used to validate uniqueness of the WarehouseLogic Receipt
The uniqueness will be validated for combination of Company Code, Customer Code, Reference Number and Active Receipt Status

This filed will be used to calculate expected and record quantities.
